- Hindi.

411
00:31:38,010 --> 00:31:41,380
Ang pag-ibig lang ang makakasagot kapag tinanong kung mahal siya nito.

412
00:31:41,380 --> 00:31:43,490
Pero sabi mo wala si Love!

413
00:31:43,490 --> 00:31:47,550
Kaya naman hindi niya masabi oo.

414
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:51,520
Darn it! Tapos sasagutin ko na lang!

415
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:54,360
Bakit halatang halata ang tanong mo?!

416
00:31:55,380 --> 00:31:59,350
Bakit ka nagtatanong ng bagay na halata? Napaka childish.

417
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:03,320
Palagi akong bata. Alam mo yun.

418
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:05,510
